        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          Project Talos provides:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300 space-y-2">
          <li>Authentication and authorization services</li>
          <li>Secure remote code execution capabilities</li>
          <li>API access for integration with third-party applications</li>
          <li>Documentation and developer resources</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-8 mb-4">3. Account Registration</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-6 mb-3">3.1 Eligibility</h3>
        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          You must be at least 18 years old to create an account. By registering, you represent that:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300 space-y-2">
          <li>All information provided is accurate and complete</li>
          <li>You will maintain the accuracy of your information</li>
          <li>You are responsible for all activity under your account</li>
          <li>You will notify us immediately of any unauthorized access</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-6 mb-3">3.2 Account Security</h3>
        
        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials. We strongly recommend enabling multi-factor authentication (MFA) for additional security.
        </p>

