        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          You may not use the Service to:
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 border border-red-200 dark:border-red-800 rounded-xl p-6 my-6">
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-red-800 dark:text-red-200 space-y-2 m-0">
            <li>Violate any applicable laws or regulations</li>
            <li>Infringe on intellectual property rights</li>
            <li>Distribute malware, viruses, or malicious code</li>
            <li>Attempt to breach security measures or gain unauthorized access</li>
            <li>Mine cryptocurrency or engage in blockchain activities</li>
            <li>Send spam or unsolicited communications</li>
            <li>Interfere with other users' access to the Service</li>
            <li>Use the Service for any illegal purpose</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-6 mb-3">4.2 Code Execution Restrictions</h3>
        
        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          When using the code execution service, you agree not to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300 space-y-2">
          <li>Attempt to escape the sandbox environment</li>
          <li>Access the network or file system outside the container</li>
          <li>Execute code that could harm our infrastructure</li>
          <li>Use excessive resources beyond your plan limits</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-8 mb-4">5. Payment Terms</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-6 mb-3">5.1 Subscription Plans</h3>
        
        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          We offer multiple subscription tiers with different feature sets and usage limits. Details are available on our <a href="/#pricing" class="text-olive-leaf-600 hover:underline">pricing page</a>.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-6 mb-3">5.2 Billing</h3>
        
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300 space-y-2">
          <li>Subscriptions are billed in advance on a monthly or annual basis</li>
          <li>All fees are exclusive of taxes, which you are responsible for paying</li>
          <li>Failed payments may result in service suspension</li>
          <li>You may upgrade or downgrade your plan at any time</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-6 mb-3">5.3 Refunds</h3>
        
        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee for new subscriptions. Refund requests must be submitted within 30 days of the initial payment.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-8 mb-4">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-6 mb-3">6.1 Our Rights</h3>
        
        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
