        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-6 mb-3">6.2 Your Content</h3>
        
        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          You retain ownership of any code, data, or content you submit to the Service. By submitting content, you grant us a limited license to process it solely for the purpose of providing the Service.
