        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          We strive to maintain 99.9% uptime for paid plans. If we fail to meet this commitment, you may be eligible for service credits as outlined in our SLA documentation.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-8 mb-4">8. Termination</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-6 mb-3">8.1 By You</h3>
        
        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          You may terminate your account at any time through the dashboard or by contacting support. Upon termination, your data will be handled according to our Privacy Policy.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-6 mb-3">8.2 By Us</h3>
        
