          We may suspend or terminate your account for violations of these Terms, fraudulent activity, or other conduct we deem harmful to the Service or other users.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-8 mb-4">9. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        
