        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-8 mb-4">13. Contact Information</h2>
        
        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          For questions about these Terms, please contact us:
        </p>
        
